{"tid":1343712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"圖解元朗郊遊好去處-南邊圍","createTime":"2019-07-21T19:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:38:00.000Z","uid":16034,"like":100,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"37011fb8d2a0ea1ea66a16991379de43789051d9","tid":1343712,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:17:36.000Z","msg":"夢見元朗有個好好嘅郊遊地點叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">南邊圍</span></span></span>，不過香港人咁繁忙，真係少有郊遊機會架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為左避免大家唔識路，我地緊係要睇清楚地圖先好去啦，而家又多唔知咩人<br />\n<br />\n南邊圍就係元朗西鐵站西北面，附近仲有唔同村，例如西邊圍、東頭村咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iuKe3gG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiuKe3gG.png&h=559f341e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁等我地開始睇下有咩景點一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.南邊圍福德堂</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Modb5wd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModb5wd.png&h=9ab605a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n村嘅堂口嚟，可以當係村公所，用嚟宣布重要嘅村務，唔好錯過呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.南邊圍圍門</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCtLqwB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCtLqwB.png&h=22a6b62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩側有「南州冠冕 邊邑弦歌」嘅對聯，圍門係圍村嘅重要象徵嚟，唔好整到人地個圍門，唔係成條村都比人笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.南邊圍村外南亭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJE3caw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJE3caw.png&h=5ac3ebd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n村民日常聚集好去處，千奇唔好搞到人無左個吹水飲酒嘅地方呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4.南邊圍神廳</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MV8vBEp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMV8vBEp.png&h=d1a70bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">南邊圍無一間真係祠堂，所以神廳就用嚟村內祭祀，位置係圍門直行到尾，大家記住抱住誠心去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上係南邊圍重點推介景點，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當然圍村仲有大量潛建景點，大家都不妨留意下啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">郊遊嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />緊係得閒先去啦，幾時夠人成團幾時去呀，不過郊外多蚊叮蟲咬，一定要做好預防措施先好去</span>"},{"pid":"c15773cb9584a90b5b4ba996fcd680426e128cdf","tid":1343712,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e77b8f6330c1e508812ef8515080cf2e35c22f","tid":1343712,"uid":255635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:19:19.000Z","msg":"一直都好想了解下新界嘅鄉村文化<br />\n係時候喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdf52c1a410dc723fb8b722a41cfaf2acd5cf3a","tid":1343712,"uid":1752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:20:05.000Z","msg":"郊遊好地點 值得支持"},{"pid":"0bf2e2639591e6cd94ae3fbb36ac4cc4ae6c562a","tid":1343712,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:20:16.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 棍問下有咩蚊怕水係最撚毒 最好可以秒殺個d"},{"pid":"b3af01dc0b7cb2cdc70783135d6ef05e92cedb26","tid":1343712,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:20:50.000Z","msg":"Push push"},{"pid":"1ab0477fea90f07e350e47a2e05f757d6ff862f7","tid":1343712,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:21:38.000Z","msg":"Push push"},{"pid":"d07b07dc0dcf2f19ca854506d545a6ea009be686","tid":1343712,"uid":279391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":