 style=\"color: red;\">南邊圍</span></span></span>，不過香港人咁繁忙，真係少有郊遊機會架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為左避免大家唔識路，我地緊係要睇清楚地圖先好去啦，而家又多唔知咩人<br />\n<br />\n南邊圍就係元朗西鐵站西北面，附近仲有唔同村，例如西邊圍、東頭村咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iuKe3gG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiuKe3gG.png&h=559f341e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁等我地開始睇下有咩景點一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.南邊圍福德堂</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Modb5wd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModb5wd.png&h=9ab605a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n村嘅堂口嚟，可以當係村公所，用嚟宣布重要嘅村務，唔好錯過呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.南邊圍圍門</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCtLqwB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCtLqwB.png&h=22a6b62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩側有「南州冠冕 邊邑弦歌」嘅對聯，圍門係圍村嘅重要象徵嚟，唔好整到人地個圍門，唔係成條村都比人笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.南邊圍村外南亭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJE3caw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJE3caw.png&h=5ac3ebd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n村民日常聚集好去處，千奇唔好搞到人無左個吹水飲酒嘅地方呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4.南邊圍神廳</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MV8vBEp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMV8vBEp.png&h=d1a70bcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">南邊圍無一間真係祠堂，所以神廳就用嚟村內祭祀，位置係圍門直行到尾，大家記住抱住誠心去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上係南邊圍重點推介景點，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當然圍村仲有大量潛建景點，大家都不妨留意下啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">郊遊嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />緊係得閒先去啦，幾時夠人成團幾時去呀，不過郊外多蚊叮蟲咬，一定要做好預防措施先好去</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a45ec69e196175591465e525cf7aaef0bec305","tid":1343712,"uid":271104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42e62f66eec0be5c9ce8acaaa7f74bca12c4a33e","tid":1343712,"uid":271104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9977b8c9024e5afb7ae881419cc22513a6e00b7","tid":1343712,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b05080248e0d18239f246e6bc0d41d7f9e305d","tid":1343712,"uid":271104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:41:23.000Z","msg":"火燒祠堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:43:05.000Z","msg":"我地唔鼓勵大家犯法架，去睇下渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"我純粹係諗到⋯咪講句火燒祠堂渣<br />\n但將來既事 邊個會估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:49:26.000Z","msg":"而且南邊圍無祠堂架嘛 得神廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2c22f85c20f5852c3099b66f026cafced1baec","tid":1343712,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T19:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />神廳"},{"pid":"5a2b63d84b2a13681739d484097d1959607fdb41","tid":1343712,"uid":15245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀！"},{"pid":"a3976bbc2a385baff3a763953b506b5a39866aaf","tid":1343712,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:36:09.000Z","msg":"推"},