f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce04e240c5123377460f87ef77be0d553a0d4c76","tid":1343712,"uid":284485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:20:45.000Z","msg":"點解冇人提，<br />\n西鐵停咗喺元朗站三十分鐘唔開，<br />\n搞到乘客焗住比人打？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;約晚上11時20分，停在月台逾30分鐘的列車終開出，目擊者稱列車車門開合3次後駛走，而列車駛離元朗站時車長並無作任何特別廣播，只有既定錄音「小心車門」。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n【元朗黑夜】目擊者：30分鐘内屢按車廂緊急通話按鈕　但無人回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/354608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F354608&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXci3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=b26abadc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/354608</a>"},{"pid":"13ff35a68388c760fa6684006daf62325b40ee85","tid":1343712,"uid":74254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:23:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dda7e29b07a7e91dd0d86e1e9a3cd04a68f5414a","tid":1343712,"uid":152228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dd1e57fe0d101e2e0e7cf4c00325a769dfe7112","tid":1343712,"uid":269495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a3e1556cad517025b8beca750cc59bfa5ac120e","tid":1343712,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"７２１上環黑警無預警射示威者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727元朗</span>"},{"pid":"b3449a6bbc15424ca46478dc168346d1704de320","tid":1343712,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549988f8776b90c51c33519cfcd0ce1aa528fce8","tid":1343712,"uid":282980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"西邊圍同南邊圍兩條村唔啱牙既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c85eba4d7ce6777c4398567ba272546dc75c88","tid":1343712,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 小弟嘅白宮聯署差四分一人咋<br />\n希望request國際人道救援/援助 人權監察<br />\n已經有七萬四千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住confirm email<br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7ce925012499c63f33854a5c217f4a9626ce0d","tid":1343712,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:56:06.000Z","msg":".我仲以為係D周圍草地周地牛屎既地方添"}]}